products.name: yogurt

products.name: butter
products.description: Butter is a dairy product made by churning cream or milk until it reaches a solid state. It is commonly used as a cooking and baking ingredient to add flavor, moisture, and richness to dishes. Butter is primarily composed of milk fat and contains trace amounts of protein and vitamins.

products.name: cream
